{
  "texts": [
    "It continues its analysis by isolating chunks related to other elements such as the Exclusive Gateway and the Send Task.",
    "EmbeddingThe embedding phase plays a crucial role in the representation of the input data, aiming to transform the process model chunks generated in the chunking step into process model embeddings.",
    "The process model chunks are transformed into a numerical format that can be efficiently processed and stored in a vector database.",
    "Notably, the embedding phase transforms the raw input into dense, low-dimensional vectors, capturing semantic information and contextual relationships.",
    "These embeddings serve as the foundation for downstream tasks, such as retrieval and generation, in the pipeline."
  ]
}